</emphasis>
centr.: İÇEL (= 
<collectingRegion box="[639,716,1173,1197]" country="Turkey" name="Mersin" pageId="4" pageNumber="7">Mersin</collectingRegion>
) province, Erdemli (
<geoCoordinate box="[930,1020,1171,1197]" degrees="36" direction="north" minutes="37" orientation="latitude" pageId="4" pageNumber="7" precision="925" value="36.616665">36°37′N</geoCoordinate>
